      "review_summary": "The PR changes Nextcloud Talk webhook decoding to parse JSON before schema validation, acknowledge schema mismatches with 200/no dispatch, keep malformed JSON on 400, and update replay tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +11, Tests +29. Total +40 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. The underlying bug is source-reproducible because signed non-message Talk events fail the strict current schema and return 400, and the PR regression is source-reproducible because the updated fixture changes a malformed Create/Note payload to 200.",
